# Cloud Optimisation & Accountability Communications Plan

This plan details to the who, how and when we will communicate information to users and stakeholders.

## The Plan

The table below sets out the typical types of communications the Team want to issue.

| What information                                    | Target Audience                 | When                                                                                       | Channel                                                         |
| --------------------------------------------------- | ------------------------------- | ------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------ | --------------------------------------------------------------- |
| New features or services                            | All stakeholder and users       | As features are shipped                                                                    | #finops-greenops-community                                      |
| Things we have learned                              | Justice Digital, Data & Science | Regularly when we have key things to show or promote                                       | Show the Thing                                                  |
| Things we have learned                              | OCTO                            | Quarterly                                                                                  | OCTO All Hands                                                  |
| Things we have learned                              | OCTO                            | Quarterly                                                                                  | OCTO All Hands                                                  |
| Sharing successes                                   | Chief Technology Officer        | Weekly                                                                                     | #octo-team                                                      |
| Sharing successes                                   | SMT                             | Monthly                                                                                    | Check-in                                                        |
| Sharing successes                                   | Justice Digital, Data & Science | Regularly when we have key things to show or promote                                       | Post about them in #chat on Slack/Consider for a Show the Thing |
| FinOps & GreenOps Blogs and News                    | All stakeholder and users       | Regularly when we have key things to show or promote                                       | #finops-greenops-community                                      |

There may be occasions where we want to publish something to the wider MOJ or the Public. In these instances we can publish something on the [Justice, Digital, Data and Science blog](https://mojdigital.blog.gov.uk/). Requests to publish on the blog should be made to #ask-comms in the first instance.
